{"tid":1618331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於宵禁 (唔好俾人帶風向）","createTime":"2019-10-04T05:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T06:02:58.000Z","uid":157926,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a7cadd536db27f6e83abcdbd0a2ee4805708a731","tid":1618331,"uid":157926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:25:35.000Z","msg":"其實大家有冇諗過呢幾日不斷有新聞講話政府會用緊急法去修訂蒙面法。，但係啱啱開連登就見到關於宵禁嘅消息。<br />\n<br />\n會唔會有機會連登俾人帶咗風向，等到真係有蒙面法嗰陣大家嘅反應唔會咁大。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">中國人總是喜歡折衷、求和<br />\n你說屋裏太暗要打開一個窗，<br />\n他們肯定打死都不願<br />\n如果你說將屋頂拆了、<br />\n他們又會同意打開一個窗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命、光復香港</span>"},{"pid":"9e572943d0f59110e09aa47d441665b83b9005a2","tid":1618331,"uid":157926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:25:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb890b982631242b7f25393e0edceaa5217dbbd6","tid":1618331,"uid":157926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:26:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52dfe457ecc022e4905c15762877f692f38e0c03","tid":1618331,"uid":213977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:26:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ba450550d811eb7fd1983c4501661145e65404c","tid":1618331,"uid":157926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d70ad860118f574f105307660151506bcfff75a","tid":1618331,"uid":157926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:27:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfe75967a53ab7eb4b31bed73d0d4e9828956dac","tid":1618331,"uid":157926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:28:05.000Z","msg":"好重要呀推！"},{"pid":"fe05c34ad17dc2a1c4e82b3149af554fe4354078","tid":1618331,"uid":26015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,